{"tid":2323642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府鬼祟澄清無採購輝瑞貨","createTime":"2020-12-13T10:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T11:31:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"13816ef9e174170f9c5815deaebd22f09faa7251","tid":2323642,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/FCMM22UI55DMZBFMRCX76VRKGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FFCMM22UI55DMZBFMRCX76VRKGE%2F&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mdOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=91b36d09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FFCMM22UI55DMZBFMRCX76VRKGE%2F&h=9bd04a23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/FCMM22UI55DMZBFMRCX76VRKGE/</a><br />\n<br />\n政府鬼祟澄清無採購輝瑞貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/23XumG5cWCtvRKOWjuOcShR6PTs=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K2GTRADXF5HEXFFGGYCXNBMUDI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F23XumG5cWCtvRKOWjuOcShR6PTs%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK2GTRADXF5HEXFFGGYCXNBMUDI.jpg&h=cccef8c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■政府深夜出稿，澄清輝瑞為德國BioNTech中國以外的合作夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「某一個人說話有冇份量，你會唔會信，都要諗吓呢個人有咩前科，呢個特別人士有咩前科？我唔需要喺呢度重複。」特首林鄭月娥周五發放誤導公眾訊息，訛稱港府與輝瑞藥廠達成協議，深夜才發出新聞稿鬼祟更正輝瑞僅屬復星與德國藥廠BioNTech的合作夥伴，至昨晚又再發稿，表示復星供應的疫苗將於歐洲生產。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：老翁猝死 家屬確診  殮房遺體補檢測 始揭染疫<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥前日訛稱，政府已與兩間疫苗製造商達成協議，包括美國輝瑞藥廠。至前晚深夜11時，食衞局出稿講述採購疫苗安排，字裏行間澄清<span class=\"orange\">「輝瑞為BioNTech中國大陸及港澳台地區以外區域的合作夥伴」</span>，港府的商談對象其實是復星與德國藥廠BioNTech。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始昨日在港台節目上解畫，政府主要與內地的復星醫藥、德國BioNTech商討及洽購該疫苗，「當然呢一個疫苗都係三間藥廠連埋輝瑞一齊研發，但係我哋去傾呢個協議，主要都係同復星傾，所以我哋主要都係提返復星同BioNTech。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：撐國貨 林鄭稱帶頭打疫苗  專家不建議採購：無數據難證品質<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指與復星協議 再購750萬劑<br />\n<br />\n至昨晚，食衞局再發出新聞稿，針對公眾對內地疫苗的戒心，表示港府與復星醫藥達成協議，將會取得最多750萬劑由復星與德國藥廠BioNTech合作研發的mRNA疫苗（即BNT162b2），供港的疫苗將於歐洲生產。第一批100萬劑量預計最快可於明年第一季交付。<br />\n<br />\n香港醫院藥劑師學會會長崔俊明表示，根據世衞資料，BNT162b2疫苗是由BioNtech、輝瑞及復星三方共同研發，而復星是大中華分銷商，因此港府主要與復星商討採購事宜。復星負責大中華地區的臨床研究、上市申請及銷售等，而BioNtech負責提供做臨床研究的原材料等所需，相信政府因商業運作而需「正名」，註明輝瑞只是BioNtech為中國及港澳台以外地區的合作夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n立法會前議員、公民黨郭家麒說，政府「係唔係誤導市民或者隱瞞事情，呢啲冇人知」，但事件會影響公眾信心。"},{"pid":"97a6f79d2504c52d58464164a0270084c7622a7a","tid":2323642,"uid":340088,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:24:31.000Z","msg":"全部都係垃圾"},{"pid":"7071bc253955b7321eb04df0d2d409b683c1e11d","tid":2323642,"uid":353080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"廢水 升唔起"},{"pid":"b800edffe98f78fac389ddf2cb4fd304f8b73c70","tid":2323642,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:28:09.000Z","msg":"林鄭有咩前科都唔想重複<br />\n<br />\n採購都有前科<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200703/UG5BBPWG4Q4KMZBO3FYSNL5ZCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FUG5BBPWG4Q4KMZBO3FYSNL5ZCQ%2F&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mdOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=4b7d65f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FUG5BBPWG4Q4KMZBO3FYSNL5ZCQ%2F&h=6ccd7d4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200703/UG5BBPWG4Q4KMZBO3FYSNL5ZCQ/</a>"},{"pid":"ef88d65c49aadaa78d998f038ec98c0d03c6b026","tid":2323642,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4496cfcc856d4dc39bc47172033571ebd47c567c","tid":23236